categories.name: avg
categories.description: The average number of times the batter reached successfully on base due to a hit: hits / atBats

categories.name: homeRuns
categories.description: The number of hits that allowed the batter to round the bases and score without the aid of an error of the defense.

categories.name: RBIs
categories.description: The number of runs scored by a batter's play.

categories.name: wins
categories.description: The number of times the pitcher was attributed with a win

categories.name: ERA
categories.description: The average number of runs a pitcher yields per 9 innings thrown

categories.name: saves
categories.description: The number of times a pitcher enters and finishes the game without surrendering the lead in a save opportunity.

categories.name: strikeouts
categories.description: The number of times the pitcher struck out a batter.

categories.name: qualityStarts
categories.description: The number of quality starts for a pitcher.
